        </section>

        <section class="section card" id="faq">
          <h2>FAQ</h2>
          <p><strong>Q:</strong> Should I buy new or used?<br><strong>A:</strong> New offers warranty and less initial maintenance; used can be a great value if inspected carefully.</p>
          <p><strong>Q:</strong> How big of an RV can I handle?<br><strong>A:</strong> Start with something you feel comfortable driving. Many first-timers choose Class B or small Class C.</p>
        </section>

